    <div class="slide s2-roomy">
      <h2 class="slide-header">The Challenge We Are Facing</h2>
      <div class="slide-content">
        <div class="bullet-stack">
          <div class="bullet-point"><span class="bullet-icon">‚ñ∂</span><span><span class="highlight">15% of first-year students</span> took remedial math in 2019‚Äì20¬π</span></div>
          <div class="bullet-point"><span class="bullet-icon">‚ñ∂</span><span>Only <span class="highlight">1 in 8 students</span> use tutoring services¬≤</span></div>
          <div class="bullet-point bullet-sub"><span class="bullet-icon">‚Ä¢</span><span><span class="highlight">66% believe they do not need help</span>; 27% cite lack of time¬≥</span></div>
          <div class="bullet-point bullet-sub"><span class="bullet-icon">‚Ä¢</span><span>Barriers to help-seeking: <span class="highlight">stigma, fear, negative past experiences</span>‚Å¥</span></div>
          <div class="bullet-point"><span class="bullet-icon">‚ñ∂</span><span>Online course completion <span class="highlight">7‚Äì20 percentage points lower</span> than face-to-face‚Åµ</span></div>
          <div class="bullet-point bullet-sub"><span class="bullet-icon">‚Ä¢</span><span>Widens equity gaps: White-Black completion gap <span class="highlight">grows by ~5pp</span>‚Å∂</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="callout">
          <strong>Sources:</strong> ¬πNCES (2024); ¬≤Mowreader (2025); ¬≥Czyz et al. (2013); ‚Å¥Winograd &amp; Rust (2014); ‚ÅµHachey et al. (2022); ‚Å∂Xu &amp; Xu (2019)
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3. COMPARISON (COMPACT) -->
    <div class="slide compact">
      <h2 class="slide-header">From Live Embedded Tutors to 24/7 AI Support</h2>
      <div class="slide-content">
        <div class="comparison-grid">
          <div class="comparison-card">
            <h3 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom:14px; font-size:1.3em; font-weight:800;">Previous: Live Embedded Tutors</h3>
            <ul class="feature-list">
              <li>‚úì Dedicated support hours</li>
              <li>‚úì Virtual &amp; in-person via Teams</li>
              <li>‚úì Weekly encouragement messages</li>
